content:
Vlocity OmniAnalytics can support other third-party analytics vendors aside from Google Analytics.

These tasks are for editing and referencing a Visualforce page. To use a static resource instead, see Workflow for Using a Static Resource Instead of a Visualforce Page.

Before You Begin

Register with the third-party analytics vendor.
Copy the vendor's <script> code.
Learn about the vendor's event names and JSON payload structures.

To use a third-party analytics vendor, clone the Visualforce page for the Tracking Manager and add third-party code to it.

After creating a Tracking Manager for the third-party analytics vendor, reference it from a Tracking Configuration and Tracking Group.
title: Configuring OmniAnalytics with Third-Party Vendors
